lude swimming turtles and baby turtle spawners!\n", "short_description": "Create an interactive Zoo in your home with over 60 animals!\n- pass through enabled to see animals in your actual surroundings in mixed reality\n- animals are placeable and moveable with random spawn options and deletion options\n- variety of pre-made and customizable animal placements:\n-- full sized animals\n-- half sized animals\n-- tabletop sized animals\n- animals include: tigers, rhinos, hippos, lions, great white sharks, turtles, bears, zebras, deer, elephants, dinosaurs, birds, and more!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://zosustudios.wixsite.com/website/about", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://zosustudios.wixsite.com/website/about", "publisher_name": "ZOSU Studios LLC", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.zosustudios.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "879473995923081"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["EDUCATIONAL", "DINOSAURS", "CASUAL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8032056330203928"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031613_2111145385924860_5984541702713082355_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=34ABCGdAFnAQ7kNvgEqsP1U&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAEzOB4NlfpbJZzOZHeLgnQpLjzvpzY7bzYS9L5s0QKQw&oe=66E4180F"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "